{"product_id":"hoia-hydrating-hair-mist-100ml","title":"HOIA Hydrating Hair Mist 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePleasantly scented hydrating spray helps to keep hair healthy, strong and shiny. Spray contains locally sourced nettle extract and rice water to strengthen hair, plant-based keratin, deeply moisturizing hyaluronic acid and aloe, hair-softening seaweed extracts and plant hydrosols, nourishing oils and shine-enhancing essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake the bottle before use and spray an appropriate amount onto wet or dry hair. No need to rinse hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Salvia Officinalis Distillate water, *Achillea Millefolium Distillate water, Oryza Sativa Seed water, Chodrus Crispus extract, Sargassum Fluitans\/Natans extract, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Crambe Abyssinica Seed oil, *Nigella Sativa Seed oil, Saccharomyces Ferment, Lactobacillus Ferment, Hydronated Sodium Hyaluronate, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf juice, Sodium Levulinate, Urtica Dioica Plant extract, Pentylene Glycol, Sodium Anisate, *Lavandula Angustifolia oil, *Pelargonium Graveolens oil, Citric Acid. **Citral, **Geraniol, **Linalool, **Limonene, **Citronellol. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic. **Natural components of essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324565688647,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-hydrating-hair-mist-100ml-963057.jpg?v=1739897245","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hoia-hydrating-hair-mist-100ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}